title: Where Do We Go From Here?! China's Infiltration of American Culture EXPOSED!
description: From Hollywood to COVID-19 to Joe Biden, China has been getting its hands on every aspect of American culture. We expose how and why that’s a problem. Also, this may surprise you, but Biden’s nominee to lead the ATF is a complete imbecile when it comes to guns. With special guest RUDY GULIANI.
